{"tid":1723264,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"知唔知點解大家咁憎, 咁不滿FA？","createTime":"2019-11-15T06:47:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T09:46:44.000Z","uid":162344,"like":23,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"12f5734346a47041b71ebb32ce3f70caad1f0045","tid":1723264,"uid":162344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:47:26.000Z","msg":"知唔知點解大家咁憎, 咁不滿FA？<br />\n<br />\n中大有護理同醫科生，poly自己有護理科,加上有紅十字會<br />\n使乜要咁多FA<br />\n仲要勁多上完三十個鐘， 著住件公廁EMS反光衫就當自己係醫生嘅非poly，非CU人士。<br />\n<br />\n之前見班垃圾FA爆曬中大 保安車做救護車,<br />\n入嚟玩mario， 不停喺二號橋同四條柱度來回都唔知做乜， 有傷者咩？<br />\n 入到嚟poly，係G core 果度又搶車玩<br />\n<br />\n成日無所事事, 喺校園內食煙<br />\n我屌你老母呀！！喺我屋企食煙！！ 死出去外面食啦<br />\n<br />\nCU車禍仲要好似有3 team FA 搶Case <br />\n仲要屌真mo， 仲要講：唔關事嘅人走開， 唔好阻住我哋做嘢。 同黑警有咩分別？<br />\n<br />\n成班FA 爆撚曬PolyU podium啲房, 自己瞓， 喺度播片， 有冇諗過出面嘅人好辛苦咁備戰緊架<br />\n光環撚Max同佢條古怪team又係度， 成班人不知所謂<br />\n當而家嘉年華party？？"},{"pid":"82376ba4bccae9496e48cd43fd4f92f3a6009b6b","tid":1723264,"uid":159997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:48:39.000Z","msg":"無人打撚柒個Max?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb5f504f849718a2fcb88cbf4f07b402459fd71a","tid":1723264,"uid":112416,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:49:25.000Z","msg":"分化撚？"},{"pid":"91421d13090ff7695af7bf2389acb0900078ad56","tid":1723264,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:49:54.000Z","msg":"[轉守為攻] 將大學要塞化，無限伸展，連結18區開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1722759\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1722759</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e4daf945f9c4fbb9416a46a3ac16745d9b55ff3b","tid":1723264,"uid":75953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:50:07.000Z","msg":"所以呢? 想任合FA 唔出黎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1bf2236b9f1c799c9b7ca5f2248a295a135d6e","tid":1723264,"uid